BLESSED BE PHILIPP
BLESSED BE SCOTT

SHAPES WHICH MAKE
UP ALL THE THINGS
OF OUR CREATIONS.

STATES AND LINES OF
SCRIPT, FOR THEY
POWER AND MOVE ALL
OF OUR CREATIONS.

IVE JUS TYPED STUFF IN SO
THIS LOOKS MORE IMPRESS
IVE FROM FURTHER OFF.
WALL OF TEXT INCOMING,
NO MEANING TO BE GLEAM-
ED FROM HERE, PURE EYE
DISTRACTION.
GO ON WASTING YOUR LIFE
READING THIS SINCE IVE

YEAH, STUFF AND THINGS
AND OTHER THINGS.
THEN MORE THINGS, AMEN.
